org.chronos.chronograph.api.structure

Interface ChronoElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Element
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ChronoEdge, ChronoVertex
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractChronoElement, AbstractElementProxy, ChronoEdgeImpl, ChronoEdgeProxy, ChronoVertexImpl, ChronoVertexProperty, ChronoVertexProxy

    public interface ChronoElement
extends org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Element
    A ChronoElement is a ChronoGraph-specific extension of the general TinkerPop Element class.

    This interface defines additional methods for all graph elements, mostly intended for internal use only.
